{"tid":1224571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長輩圖攻勢係時候開拓第二條戰線！","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:18:09.000Z","uid":190579,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6496bc2a1f0924651cbfd05688f7ae9e25888e","tid":1224571,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">行動</span></span><br />\n去公園，圖書館，酒樓等地airdrop 長輩圖！改個似老人家既iPhone 名，每隔十幾二十分鐘一次，次次用唔同名。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">理由</span></span><br />\n時至今日，相信自己人身邊既親朋戚朋，同埋佢哋既親朋戚友都已經睇過。<br />\n<br />\n信既已經信左，唔信既再同佢嘈都冇意思。所以我建議開第二條戰線，用air drop 將長輩圖腥比街上面既長輩，擴大戰果。<br />\n<br />\n由老人家既角度出發：<br />\n<br />\n好多老人家最<span style=\"color: red;\">唔信</span>既就係自己屋企人，而<span style=\"color: green;\">最信</span>既，就係一齊買餸飲茶識既三菇六婆。<br />\n<br />\nD 長輩圖由平時成日同自己嘈，比政黨同外國操縱既後生仔send 過嚟，未睇已經打左六折。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，多個渠道收到既消息更有說服力。如果佢哋係飲緊茶，排緊免費報紙，周圍都係其他老人家時收到長輩圖，可信性一定高好多！"},{"pid":"1c0c530be7f5ee343a25ee195908f6a47455bb61","tid":1224571,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d1040d4021b4d56c13b368f527118925741b70","tid":1224571,"uid":8007,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"傳送門教iphone 改名：<br />\nSettings &gt; General &gt; About.<br />\nTap the first line, which shows the name of your device.<br />\nRename your device, then tap Done."},{"pid":"e4803ec9466f222352a6fb2522b047b39093245c","tid":1224571,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"d廢老都唔用iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試左成朝都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2ee07b1f947de6408bf884061a46b8828e3254","tid":1224571,"uid":71509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"馬會都係<br />\n<br />\n有直播足球就多人"},{"pid":"55d2653315b892733ae901bd669d113a98eef2a7","tid":1224571,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4803ec9466f222352a6fb2522b047b39093245c","tid":1224571,"uid":228294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:11:48.000Z","msg":"d廢老都唔用iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試左成朝都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"你試下去人口密度高既地方啦，事半功倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啱先去圖書館見到大量廢老先靈機一觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nair drop 左十幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}